T02TD3390E:56a-1: ha ya gr'i ba s'a dha nam /
T02TD3390E:56a-3: rta mgrin gyi sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD3390E:56a-4: dpal rta mgrin la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3390E:56a-5: sngon du bstan pa'i cho gas sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma la h'um dmar po'i ye shes las yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'phags pa rta mgrin mdog dmar ba /
T02TD3390E:56a-8: zhal so so nas spyan gsum gsum mo //
T02TD3390E:56a-9: sngon po dang dkar po ni g-yas dang cig gos kyi zhal lo //
T02TD3390E:56a-10: sbrul gyi rgyan can 'gying bag gis gnon cing gnas pa /
T02TD3390E:56a-11: khro bo'i lta stangs kyis gzigs pa /
T02TD3390E:56b-2: mche ba gnyis kyis ma mchu btsir ba /
T02TD3390E:56b-4: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can no //
T02TD3390E:56b-5: rdo rje dang dbyug pa dang /
T02TD3390E:56b-7: mda' 'phyar ba ni g-yas pa'i phyag bzhi na'o //
T02TD3390E:56b-8: sdigs mdzub dang rang gi nu ma bzung ba dang /
T02TD3390E:56b-9: padma dang gzhu 'phyar ba ni g-yon gyi phyag bzhi na'o //
T02TD3390E:56b-10: mi bskyod pas mnan pa'i dbu rgyan can bsam par bya'o zhes bya ba ni rta mchog ye shes rdo rje zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin to //
T02TD3390E:56b-12: aom ha ya gr'i ba sv'a h'a /
T02TD3390E:56b-13: rta mgrin gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3390E:56b-14: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3390E:56b-15: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o //
